ECM Real Estate Administrator Proposes Liquidation, CTK Says

-- B y   L e n k a   P o n i k e l s k a
-- 
2011-07-19T10:11:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-19/ecm-real-estate-administrator-proposes-liquidation-ctk-says.html
ECM Real Estate Investment AG’s
administrator, Ivo Halla, proposed liquidating the Czech
developer, which has been in insolvency proceedings since May,
 CTK  reported, citing a filing from the insolvency registry web
site.  ECM’s management is pushing through reorganization of the
debt of 2 billion koruna ($115.8 billion), the newswire added.  To contact the reporter on this story: Lenka Ponikelska in
Prague   lponikelska1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at   jagomez@bloomberg.net  